Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.95,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Brzo, brzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:19.99,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Drago mi je što si se konačno oporavila.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:27.58,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemoj da se brineš što tek sada počinješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:32.01,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Druželjubivi su, sigurno ćeš se lako uklopiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:39.87,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Da...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:53.53,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobro, slušajte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:01:01.03,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Učenica Nišijama, koja je bila odsutna od početka školske godine, je došla u školu danas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:04.29,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa, hajde da nam se predstavi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:06.92,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Mitan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.32,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nema nikoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:11.93,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:17.67,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...? Nišijama?! Gde si nestala?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:25.85,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ja sam Nišijama Hijori i petnaest mi je godina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:28.48,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ekstremno sam stidljiva!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:30.48,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nišijama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:34.98,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.09,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijori!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:46.50,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa, izvoli, predstavi se.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:49.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ovaj... pa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:50.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Vau!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:51.18,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kul!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:52.78,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Malecka je!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:54.00,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kako je slatka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:59.68,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stvari kao što su predstavljanja... su stvari koje mrzim najviše u životu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:03.35,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ali sada kada sam ovde...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:07.56,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trebalo bi barem svoje ime da kažem!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:09.47,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ni...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:11.89,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nišijama Hijo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:15.94,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobro jutro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:19.04,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, hej, šta je smešno?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.87,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kasniš, Jušine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:24.46,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Opet kasniš, Hirose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:27.76,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nišijama nam se upravo predstavljala.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.54,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Prekinuo me je u pola reči...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:31.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nišijama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:40.44,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Šta je sa ovom osobom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:48.20,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nisi li ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.65,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...pomalo malecka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:54.73,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Neverovatna razlika u visini!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.72,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Vau!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.28,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ričan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:07.37,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tako mi je drago što si ti u ovom odeljenju!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:11.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Polako, polako. Zar ti nije drago što nisi morala da ponavljaš godinu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.12,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.75,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ali baš nemaš sreće.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:19.09,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dan pre školske ceremonije, udario te je kamion...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.76,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...što je za posledicu imalo slomljene kosti po celom telu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:29.02,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Da sam bila pregažena, ne bih sada bila ovde, pa sam možda zapravo i imala sreće.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:33.02,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kako se snalaziš sa učenjem? Već je decembar...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:36.31,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U redu je. Uzimala sam časove privatno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:39.53,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takođe, iz bolnice su me pustili na par dana kako bih mogla da polažem testove.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:46.45,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kada pričamo o sreći i nesreći... Momak do mene...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.70,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta je bilo, Jušin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:55.38,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ništa. Samo sam zapanjen što postoje srednjoškolke takve mikroskopske veličine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.26,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ali i ti si prilično visok, znaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:04.55,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nego, razmišljao sam kako me Nišijama podseća na nešto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.18,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta bi to moglo da bude?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:12.81,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta? Hijori te podseća na neku glumicu možda?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:13.87,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:17.56,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}hijoko = pile
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:17.56,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Haha, Hijoko!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.67,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hi-jo-ko"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:24.07,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Znaš, svo umiljato i pufnasto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.53,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tako nekako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.99,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Želim da je pomazim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.50,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Prekini, bre...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.16,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Jušine, perverznjaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.75,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nišijama, sakrij se negde!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:37.96,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:44.51,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja sam... Nišijama Hijori...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.80,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bože, molim te, spasi me od ove neotesane osobe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:56.81,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dovoljno mi je teško što moram da krenem u školu usred školske godine, i još i on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:58.86,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ustanite!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.65,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta ste vas dvoje, džin i patuljak?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.28,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Baš je malecka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.91,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Baš je visok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.66,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima pola metra razlike između njih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.58,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On samo nepotrebno privlači pažnju i na mene!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:21.24,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Spava svo vreme tokom časova i hrče glasno!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:26.68,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I taman kada sam pomislila da konačno pazi na času...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:34.14,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Prvi put vidim nekoga da jede na času!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:35.89,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I to tako brzo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.35,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Videla si me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.61,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sada si i ti saučesnica.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.35,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoćeš i ti malo, Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:57.62,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nastavniče! Hirose i Nišijama jedu usred časa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.54,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka, smrade jedan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.50,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nišijama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.67,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta, već ste u takvom odnosu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.34,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nije tako!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.38,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Prekinite... Zar ne vidite da je pocrvenela?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.26,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Već na prvi dan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:14.60,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo, Nišijama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:17.52,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Šta je sa njime?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:23.94,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Iako ja želim miran život... Iako ne želim da odudaram...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.36,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Školska kuhinja
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.44,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Zašto ti se ne sviđa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.90,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Jušin je popularan, znaš...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.63,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...i dobar je momak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:36.58,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Zato mi se ne sviđa. Pošto je on tu, ljudi se okupljaju oko njegove klupe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.38,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:42.42,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...i onda čak pričaju i sa mnom koja sedim do njega.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.94,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Hijori, tako si slatka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.09,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Koliko si visoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:49.80,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O čemu pričaš sa Jušinom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:57.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Trebalo bi jednostavno da se sprijateljiš sa svima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:03.19,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijori! Ovo je prilika da savladaš svoju stidljivost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:07.74,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bile smo zajedno od vrtića...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:13.16,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...ali jednog dana ćemo morati da se razdvojimo. Šta ćeš raditi kada dođe do toga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:15.62,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ričan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.82,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne želim da se razdvojimo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:22.33,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Samo sam pričala "šta bi bilo kad bi bilo", nemoj da plačeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:27.09,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A i ko zna, možda jednog dana nađeš nekoga ko ti se sviđa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:31.67,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako se plašiš sticanja prijatelja, kako ćeš se jednog dana zaljubiti?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:36.49,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne brini, Jušin je momak koji se dobro slaže sa svima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:40.89,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako se sprijateljiš sa njime, mislim da ćeš steći i nove prijatelje.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.81,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da se sprijateljim...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.75,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobro došla nazad, Hijorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:54.99,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hijorin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:57.71,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rešio sam da te zovem Hijorin. Slatko je, zar ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:08:00.45,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijo, reci nešto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.47,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ali šta da kažem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:14.55,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kada se unervozim, ne mogu ni reč da prozborim.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.05,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne brini, ne brini!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:25.94,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pitam se da li ću upspeti da se sprijateljim sa njim...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.41,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nišijama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.10,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nišijama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.07,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Da!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.20,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne moraš da prezaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.87,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Evo. Mitan mi je rekla da ti dam ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.23,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Plašiš je, Nacuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.33,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Ućuti, bre!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:50.00,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zaboravila sam da kažem "Hvala"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:01.85,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oko Hirosea uvek ima ljudi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:06.06,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Njegov osmeh uvek zrači radošću.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:11.97,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Čini se... {\alpha&HFF&}tako... daleko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.95,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Čini se... tako... {\alpha&HFF&}daleko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.03,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Čini se... tako... daleko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:23.20,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijorin, nisi ponela svoju svesku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:27.50,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bre, što nisi tako rekla ranije!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.59,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mada, ni ja nisam poneo svoju.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.55,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Književnost
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:36.72,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijorin! Tanaka je baš dobar momak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.89,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Možeš da gledaš kod mene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:41.43,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Izvini, Tanaka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:50.56,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blizu je... ne mogu ni da dišem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:09.16,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hej, Takaši! Spavaš li? Nastavi da čitaš!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:11.79,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sledeći pasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:15.13,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Znam i ovako nešto da nacrtam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:17.80,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.89,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To ne liči ni na šta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.18,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Vas dvoje, nemojte da flertujete!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.93,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nastavniče, nemojte da ste ljubomorni!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.89,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A-Ali nije tako...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:31.60,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Znači ipak možeš da se nasmešiš i preda mnom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:36.03,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mislio sam da se smeješ samo oko Ričan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.79,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Drago mi je.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.11,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On dobro opaža...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:47.37,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Znaš, Hijorin, ako se budeš smešila imaćeš sreće.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.65,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To je moja teorija.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.18,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ovde!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:05.26,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobro, i kako vam se svideo prvi dan u školi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:11.27,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Umorna? Ne brini, sutra će ti sigurno biti zabavnije!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.94,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ricuka, zakasnićemo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.31,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dolazim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:19.92,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Moram da idem. Izvini što ne možemo zajedno nazad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:22.82,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U redu je. Daj sve od sebe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:23.95,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hvala!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:30.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijori, doći ćeš u školu sutra, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:34.50,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pazi se.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:36.00,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ćao, ćao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:37.35,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ćao, ćao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:47.81,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Hijorin, ćao, ćao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.06,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidimo se!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.06,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ćao, ćao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:55.35,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zapamtile su moje ime već prvi dan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:57.65,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I to su me nazvale Hijorin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:02.53,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ako se sprijateljiš sa njime, mislim da ćeš steći i nove prijatelje.{gore}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:09.20,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Na početku sam mislila da je samo jedan bučan i neotesan momak...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.14,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Jušinova teorija.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.83,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hajde, Jušine, ideš li?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:45.99,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.24,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ćao, ćao...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ćao, ćao!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:04.80,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vidimo se sutra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.52,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(748,225)}Redari
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.52,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\frz90\pos(667,396)}Nišijama
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.52,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\frz90\pos(882,401)}Hirose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:25.07,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Danas sam redar zajedno sa Hiroseom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.62,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nišijama ne priča baš puno, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:33.59,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Slatka je.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:37.58,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ti baš voliš slatke i male stvari, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.38,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kako neko sme da bude tako malecak?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.26,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijori, dobro jutro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:47.88,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobro jutro, Ričan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:51.43,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta je ovo? Da ti se nije nešto desilo? Izgledaš srećno jutros.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.14,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:54.63,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.10,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Jušine, dobro jutro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.15,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dobro jut...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:02.36,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Jušine, pogledaj ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.10,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Glupo je, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:07.03,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stvarno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:08.76,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijori?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:13.87,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, vas dvoje ste redari danas! Ovo će ti biti odlična prilika za razgovor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:16.50,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.83,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Danas je zaspao brže nego obično.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.96,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, već je četvrti čas.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:26.92,0:14:31.26,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dnevnik
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.01,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Moraću sama da popunjavam dnevnik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.19,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, probudio se.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.89,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Jušine, preteruješ sa spavanjem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.73,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabla još nije obrisana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.73,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ko je redar danas?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.73,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, izvinjavam se!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:47.03,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ti si redar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.03,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Daj sve od sebe, Hijorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:01.95,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zašto nisam mogla da smognem snage da mu kažem...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:05.50,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...da smo danas zajedno redari i time razjasnim celu stvar?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.55,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.26,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Suknja ti se podigla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.36,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pile?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.53,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Slatko je!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:33.45,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I ja nosim takve! Te vunene su baš tople, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.49,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Jušine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.65,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kako da se ne smejem kada Hijorin ima nacrtano pile...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.65,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}pile = hijoko
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:46.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:51.92,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Jušine, zar nisi i ti redar danas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.06,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:21.29,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijorin, izađi. Svi te traže.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:30.89,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nisam trebala da dođem u školu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:42.35,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja nisam kao ti. Ja nisam neko ko lako može da se smeje svemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.90,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemoj da pričaš tako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:51.11,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemoj da govoriš "Nisam trebala da dođem."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:56.36,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konačno neko... sedi pored mene.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:02.70,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja sam uvek sedeo na tom mestu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.42,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...kako ne bih smetao drugima da vide tablu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:12.63,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nego, Hijorin, trebala si da mi kažeš da sam i ja redar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.92,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu si bila?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:25.22,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Znaš... Moje rane su se zacelile odavno...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:34.86,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ali... kako je vreme prolazilo... sve više i više sam se plašila da dođem u školu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.20,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Šta misliš da je strašnije...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.37,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Strašno je jer ne znam"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:52.42,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...ili "Strašno je jer znam"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:18:00.14,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako ne znaš, samo treba da saznaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:02.87,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lako je, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:09.47,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:18.57,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Od početka sam ja bila ta koja je postavila zid oko sebe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:21.51,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.36,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:28.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ričan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.25,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bre, gde si nestala?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.79,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Izvini, Ričan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:37.46,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Trebalo bi samo da prebiješ sve momke koji su ti se smejali; pogotovo Jušina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.11,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ovde je!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:39.74,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:40.70,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.97,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U redu, hoćemo li da se vratimo u učionicu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:47.53,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nekako mi se čini da bi baš bila šteta da se vratimo u učionicu sada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.86,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mislim, pogledajte kako je lepo napoju.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:14.01,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.42,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijori, jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:21.22,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ups, da nisam bila previše precizna možda?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:22.55,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nacuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:24.30,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Daj, pazi malo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.81,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hladno je!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.69,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ovo je prvi put da bežim sa časova,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:39.23,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}i prvi put da se smejem i pričam ovoliko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:45.95,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I prvi put...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.95,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}da sam od srca poželela da se približim nekome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:20:01.63,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bre, niko se ne vraća na čas! Ima svašta da im kažem kada se vrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.68,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, opet sam zaboravila svesku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:21.78,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-Hirose! Ovaj... Sveska...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:32.00,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Neće da se probudi... a verovatno je ni on nije poneo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.16,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Evo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:44.93,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ja sam Nišijama Hijori i petnaest mi je godina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:50.26,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I zaljubila sam se!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:58.23,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H9477FB&\b1\fs120\frz343.613\pos(805,228)}Hijokoi\N{\fs45}(Hijokoina ljubav)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:30.67,Standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stvarno nema pojma da crta.{\i0}
